MicroProject combines two kinds of code:

- An imported ProjectLibre snapshot from SourceForge, preserved under the upstream CPAL 1.0 notices found in the snapshot tree.
- New rewrite work for the Rust + Tauri application in this repository.

Upstream provenance:

- Source: https://sourceforge.net/p/projectlibre/code/ci/master/
- Imported commit: 0530be227f4a10c5545cce8d3db20ac5a4d76a66
- Import location: upstream/projectlibre-snapshot

New code written in this repository is documented as part of the MicroProject rewrite and should stay clearly separated from the imported upstream files.

